---
import ServiceLayout from '../../layouts/ServiceLayout.astro';
---

<ServiceLayout 
  title="General Dentistry" 
  category="Comprehensive Care"
  description="Complete dental care for your entire family. From preventive cleanings to restorative treatments."
  image="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1598256989800-fe5f95da9787?w=1920&h=600&fit=crop"
>
  
  <!-- Main Content -->
  <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-100 to-accent-200/50 border-l-4 border-accent-300 p-6 rounded-r-lg mb-8">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-2">Your Partner in Oral Health</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-0">
        General dentistry forms the foundation of your oral health. Our comprehensive approach focuses 
        on prevention, early detection, and conservative treatment to keep your smile healthy for life.
      </p>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-6">
      Our General Dentistry Services
    </h2>
    
    <div class="grid gap-6 mb-12">
      <!-- Preventive Care -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-6">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-primary-900 mb-4">Preventive Care</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          The best treatment is prevention. Our preventive services help you avoid dental problems 
          before they start, saving you time, money, and discomfort.
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-2">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-900 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span><strong>Professional Cleanings:</strong> Remove plaque and tartar buildup</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-900 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span><strong>Digital X-Rays:</strong> Early detection with minimal radiation</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-900 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span><strong>Oral Cancer Screening:</strong> Annual screenings for early detection</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-900 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span><strong>Fluoride Treatment:</strong> Strengthen enamel and prevent decay</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-900 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span><strong>Sealants:</strong> Protective coating for cavity-prone teeth</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Restorative Treatments -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-6">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-primary-900 mb-4">Restorative Treatments</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          When dental problems do occur, we offer conservative, effective treatments to restore 
          your teeth to their natural function and appearance.
        </p>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">Common Procedures</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-1 text-gray-600">
              <li>• Tooth-colored fillings</li>
              <li>• Dental crowns</li>
              <li>• Bridges</li>
              <li>• Root canal therapy</li>
              <li>• Tooth extractions</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">Advanced Options</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-1 text-gray-600">
              <li>• CEREC same-day crowns</li>
              <li>• Inlays and onlays</li>
              <li>• Full mouth reconstruction</li>
              <li>• TMJ treatment</li>
              <li>• Sleep apnea appliances</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Periodontal Care -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-6">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-primary-900 mb-4">Gum Disease Treatment</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          Healthy gums are essential for overall oral health. We provide comprehensive periodontal 
          care to prevent and treat gum disease at every stage.
        </p>
        <div class="bg-accent-50 rounded-lg p-4">
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">
            <strong>Did you know?</strong> Gum disease is linked to heart disease, diabetes, and other 
            systemic health conditions. Regular dental care protects more than just your smile.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-6">
      The Importance of Regular Dental Visits
    </h2>

    <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-accent-50 to-accent-100/30 rounded-2xl p-8 mb-12">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div>
          <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Every 6 Months</h4>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
            <li>✓ Professional cleaning</li>
            <li>✓ Comprehensive exam</li>
            <li>✓ Early problem detection</li>
            <li>✓ Oral cancer screening</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Annual Check-ups Include</h4>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
            <li>✓ Digital X-rays</li>
            <li>✓ Periodontal evaluation</li>
            <li>✓ Bite assessment</li>
            <li>✓ Treatment planning</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-primary-900 text-white rounded-2xl p-8">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-heading font-semibold mb-4">
        New Patient Special
      </h3>
      <p class="mb-4">
        First-time patients receive a comprehensive exam, digital X-rays, and professional cleaning 
        at a special introductory rate. Call today to learn more!
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
        <a href="#book-appointment" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-accent-300 text-primary-900 px-6 py-3 rounded-full font-medium hover:bg-accent-200 transition-colors">
          Book Your First Visit
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Related Services -->
  <div slot="related-services" class="space-y-3">
    <a href="/services/cleanings-exams" class="block p-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors">
      <h4 class="font-semibold text-dental-charcoal">Cleanings & Exams</h4>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Maintain optimal oral health</p>
    </a>
    <a href="/services/fillings" class="block p-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors">
      <h4 class="font-semibold text-dental-charcoal">Dental Fillings</h4>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Restore damaged teeth</p>
    </a>
    <a href="/services/root-canal" class="block p-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors">
      <h4 class="font-semibold text-dental-charcoal">Root Canal Therapy</h4>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Save infected teeth</p>
    </a>
  </div>

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <div slot="faq" class="space-y-6">
    <details class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
      <summary class="font-semibold text-lg cursor-pointer">How often should I visit the dentist?</summary>
      <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">
        Most patients should visit every 6 months for cleanings and check-ups. However, some patients 
        with specific conditions may need more frequent visits. We'll create a personalized schedule 
        based on your individual needs.
      </p>
    </details>
    
    <details class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
      <summary class="font-semibold text-lg cursor-pointer">What's included in a dental exam?</summary>
      <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">
        A comprehensive exam includes visual inspection of teeth and gums, oral cancer screening, 
        bite evaluation, digital X-rays (as needed), and discussion of any concerns. We'll also 
        create a treatment plan if any issues are found.
      </p>
    </details>
    
    <details class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
      <summary class="font-semibold text-lg cursor-pointer">Do you see children?</summary>
      <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">
        Absolutely! We love treating patients of all ages. We recommend bringing children for their 
        first visit by age 1 or within 6 months of their first tooth appearing. Early visits help 
        establish good oral health habits.
      </p>
    </details>

    <details class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
      <summary class="font-semibold text-lg cursor-pointer">What if I have dental anxiety?</summary>
      <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">
        We understand dental anxiety is common. Our team is trained in anxiety management techniques, 
        and we offer various comfort options including sedation dentistry. We'll work at your pace 
        to ensure a comfortable experience.
      </p>
    </details>
  </div>

</ServiceLayout>